# ğŸš€ ProServe - Modern Microservices Framework

**Build production-ready microservices with minimal code - Python decorators or YAML manifests!**

ğŸ¯ **98% Less Boilerplate â€¢ 5-Minute Start â€¢ Production Ready**

ProServe is a revolutionary microservices framework that combines the simplicity of Flask with the power of modern architecture. Create APIs, static sites, real-time chat, and more with just a few lines of code.

> ğŸš€ **Fully Modular Architecture**: All components are now modular, testable, and follow SOLID principles  
> ğŸ§ª **Comprehensive E2E Testing**: 8+ test suites covering real-world scenarios, security, performance, and integrations

## âš¡ Quick Start (3 Lines of Code!)

```python
# app.py
from proserve import Service

app = Service("my-api")

@app.endpoint("/", method="GET")
async def hello(request):
    return {"message": "Hello World! ğŸš€"}

if __name__ == "__main__":
    app.run(port=8080)
```

```bash
python app.py
# Open: http://localhost:8080
```

**That's it!** You have a production-ready API running.

> ğŸ“ **New to microservices?** Check out our [Junior Quick Start Guide](./JUNIOR_QUICK_START.md) - "ProServe in 5 minutes"

