        CORS[CORS & Security]
    end
    
    ServiceAPI --> HTTP
    ServiceAPI --> WebSocket
    ServiceAPI --> Background
    ServiceAPI --> Monitoring
    ServiceAPI --> StaticFiles
    ServiceAPI --> CORS
```

